  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220&deg;C/ 200&deg;C (fan)/ 425&deg;F/ Gas 7</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into chunky chips</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray with 1-2 tbsp <strong>olive oil</strong>, then season&nbsp;with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and oven roast for 30 min or until crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely (reserving a few leaves for garnish)</p>\r\n<p>Cube approx. 30g <span class=\"text-danger\">[60g]</span>&nbsp;<strong>butter</strong> and add to a mixing bowl with the <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>parsley</strong>, <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix and mash the <strong>butter</strong> thoroughly with a fork &ndash; this is your <strong>garlic butter</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove and discard&nbsp;the stalks from the <strong>portobello mushrooms</strong></p>\r\n<p>Divide the <strong>garlic butter</strong> between the mushrooms inside the caps</p>\r\n<p>Place the <strong>mushrooms</strong> on a separate baking tray and set aside</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p>\r\n<p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> and <strong>chopped shallot</strong> to a sheet of <strong>tin foil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Drizzle with the <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>sugar</strong> and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-4-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-4-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Scrunch the <strong>foil</strong> into a sealed package (see photo) and add to the baking tray with the mushrooms</p>\r\n<p>Put it in the oven for 15 min until the mushrooms are tender and the cherry tomatoes have softened slightly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the <strong>tomato package</strong> from the oven (leaving the mushrooms in for a further 10 min)</p>\r\n<p>Transfer the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to a small pan</p>\r\n<p>Heat gently over a medium-high heat until they break down into a warm relish (and most of the liquid has absorbed)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pan large enough to fit 4 <span class=\"text-danger\">[8]</span>&nbsp;<strong>eggs</strong> with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span>&nbsp;<strong>olive oil</strong> (you will need a lid)</p>\r\n<p>Crack the <strong>eggs</strong> into a bowl (one at a time) but do not beat</p>\r\n<p>Once&nbsp;hot, add the <strong>eggs</strong> in one go</p>\r\n<p>Add&nbsp;a lid and cook over a medium-low heat for 3 min or until the whites are cooked but the yolks are still runny&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/393__-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove&nbsp;the <strong>eggs</strong> from the heat and season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Serve the warm <strong>tomato relish</strong>, <strong>garlic herby mushrooms</strong>, <strong>chips</strong> and <strong>eggs</strong> together with the reserved <strong>parsley leaves</strong> scattered over</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
